</div></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-822-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style" ><div id="pgc-822-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell" ><div id="panel-822-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" ><div class="panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-822-1-0-0" ><div
			
			class="so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base"
			
		><h3 class="widget-title">Accounting Call Center Solutions and Answering Services – Find Your Solutions with TeleDirect</h3>
<div class="siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget">
	<p>Accounting Call Center Services | Accounting Answering Services | And Other Accounting Call Center Solutions</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>For tax consultants, accountants and financial advisors, delivering top-tier services is more than a numbers game; it’s also about providing accounting industry solutions with exceptional customer service. And sometimes, those numbers just do not add up, no matter how hard you try. You know that better customer service is better for your bottom line. But how can you keep pace with responsive accounting call center services? Let’s face it: managing a growing business is never easy, especially during tax season.</p>
<p>If you are a busy tax professional, accountant or CPA there never seems to be enough hours in the day, especially during tax season and the quarterly reporting rush. Who has time to stop in the middle of calculating numbers to answer a ringing phone?  If you and your staff are like most professionals; the answer is not you.  So, what happens to this call? Well, in most cases this call goes straight to voicemail. Not so bad, right? Wrong.</p>
<p>According to a recent American Express survey, 67% of customers have hung up the phone out of frustration they could not talk to a real person.  Can you afford to take that risk? You can’t. And your accounting call center, especially run by an experienced outsourced provider like TeleDirect, can help you avoid missed calls.</p>
<p>Customers expect their accounting answering services to deliver the same polished, professional competence that your tax and financial services provide. Nothing less than accurate, rapid, responsive customer service will do. With TeleDirect’s business process outsourcing (BPO) accounting industry solutions, your financial firm will handle all customer communications with ease and efficiency – even while you concentrate on what you do best! Let TeleDirect handle all your accounting call center solutions.</p>
<p>TeleDirect offers industry leading accounting answering services with highly trained agents and also the best technology &amp; infrastructure. We produce <a href="../../value-results/index.html">value and results</a> for each and every client with a full suite of services. Experience the difference with TeleDirect.</p>
<p>With TeleDirect’s Accounting Industry Solution you do not have to. Our 24/7/365 support gives you the peace of mind that your customers’ calls will be answered.  Our agents are here to answer your phone calls, take messages and even set appointments so you never lose business to the competition.</p>
<p><strong>Accounting Call Center &amp; Answering Services from TeleDirect: Expert, Outsourced Solutions for any Business</strong></p>
<p><a href="../../index.html">Let TeleDirect</a> help you balance the equation and put time back on your side. We’re one of the most trusted providers for the <a href="../financial-services/index.html">financial services</a> industry. And we’ll help you manage all facets of your client communication, including:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Scheduling Appointments. </strong>Your accounting answering services depend on keeping your promises to your clients. With our appointment scheduling, all of your accounting industry solutions stay on track.</li>
<li><strong>Providing answers to frequently asked questions. </strong>More than ever, accounting call center solutions  are expected to delivery accurate, timely information on a 24/7 basis. Do your accounting industry solutions provide instant FAQ responses and other automated content? If not, contact TeleDirect today.</li>
<li><strong>Urgent tax-time requests</strong>. From January to mid-April, many accounting firms and tax preparation services are overwhelmed by the sheer volume of incoming calls regarding W2 and 1099 forms, write-offs, capital gains tax, property tax, refunds and more. Ensure optimal reliability – along with satisfied clients – with TeleDirect’s flexible and robust call center platform, just one part of our complete accounting answering services.</li>
<li><strong>Year-end reporting</strong>. Whether you or your customers report on a regular calendar year cycle or fiscal year cycle, critical accounting advice never really slows down. Which means your accounting inbound call center requires significant online responsiveness. Some clients may call well after business hours – and in this case, TeleDirect’s call center platform provides everything you need, including inbound bandwidth, <a href="../../services/outbound/appointment-setting-services/index.html">appointment setting services</a> and so much more!</li>
<li><strong>Audit support</strong>. For many accountant answering services and accounting industry solutions, it’s all about being there for your clients. But what if your accounting answering services can’t keep up when it matters most? From IRS audits to random corporate audits, your clients deserve answers – and a reassuring hand – right away. If your accounting call center lacks the infrastructure and intuition to deliver on your promises, the PR damage can negatively impact your business for years to come. That’s why TeleDirect’s business process outsourcing (BPO) call center services are used by accounting call centers everywhere; they trust our service, and in turn, their customers can trust them!</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Accounting Answering Services</strong></p>
<p>TeleDirect has a complete, customized accounting answering services solution ready to launch today! Beyond our robust accounting call center solutions, we also help promote your brand and solidity your current client base. Strengthen your customer communication platform today and give our accounting call center experts a call at (800) 776-1081, or fill out our <a href="../../contact-us/index.html">client contact form</a>. We’re here to help give your accounting call center all the help it needs – and even build one from scratch, if your accounting answering services doesn’t have one!</p>
<p>If you need accounting call center solutions for accountants or assistance with your accounting inbound call center, contact TeleDirect today. Experience the difference with our BPO call center platform!</p>
